Enum Class Date.Month

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Date.Month>
fitnessclubgui.fitnessclub.Date.Month
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Date.Month>, Constable
Enclosing class:
Date
private static enum Date.Month extends Enum<Date.Month>
This enum represents the valid months and days for the Date Class. Each month has a month value and the amount of days associated with that month.
